com.communote.server.web.fe.widgets.controls

Class MultiViewTabWidget

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.server.widgets.AbstractWidget
      • com.communote.server.web.fe.widgets.controls.MultiViewTabWidget
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Widget

    public class MultiViewTabWidget
extends AbstractWidget
    Server side class for the MultiViewTabWidget that is a tab control which contains one content. A tab-click typically results in rendering another view of the content.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
